{"type":"text","timestamp":1775853620429,"sessionID":"ses_286e216f3ffe42B0Yxi3p5SwW2","part":{"id":"prt_d791f9cfb001TjhW2jI0m7EU9l","messageID":"msg_d791f92780019KzqfVrCWad45y","sessionID":"ses_286e216f3ffe42B0Yxi3p5SwW2","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API (client-go)\n\n### Summary\nThe implementation **partially matches** the spec. Core functionality is working (tests pass), but several elements differ from the specification.\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Matching Requirements\n\n| Component | Spec | Implementation | Status |\n|-----------|------|----------------|--------|\n| **Clientset.Interface** | `RuntimeV1alpha1()` method | Present (`clientset.go:22`) | ✅ |\n| **Clientset constructors** | `NewForConfig`, `NewForConfigOrDie`, `New` | Present (`clientset.go:26-63`) | ✅ |\n| **RuntimeV1alpha1Interface** | `RESTClient()`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter` | Matches (`runtime_client.go:17-21`) | ✅ |\n| **AgentRuntimeInterface** | All CRUD methods (Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, DeleteCollection, Get, List, Watch, Patch) | All present (`agentruntime.go:15-26`) | ✅ |\n| **CodeInterpreterInterface** | Same methods as AgentRuntime | All present (`codeinterpreter.go:15-26`) | ✅ |\n| **REST resource** | `agentruntimes` | Uses `\"agentruntimes\"` (`agentruntime.go:48`) | ✅ |\n| **REST resource** | `codeinterpreters` | Uses `\"codeinterpreters\"` (`codeinterpreter.go:53`) | ✅ |\n| **SchemeGroupVersion** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` | Correct (`register.go:15`) | ✅ |\n| **APIPath** | `/apis` | Correct (`runtime_client.go:62`) | ✅ |\n| **NegotiatedSerializer** | From scheme | Uses `scheme.Codecs.WithoutConversion()` (`runtime_client.go:63`) | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Differences from Spec\n\n| Component | Spec Requirement | Implementation | Severity |\n|-----------|-----------------|---------------|----------|\n| **Clientset.Interface** | `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` | Missing | Medium |\n| **Clientset struct** | Embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and `runtimeV1alpha1 *RuntimeV1alpha1Client` | Uses `ClientsetInner` with `*RuntimeV1alpha1` | Low |\n| **Constructors** | `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client)` | Missing | Medium |\n| **AgentRuntimeInterface** | `AgentRuntimeExpansion` marker | Missing | Low |\n| **CodeInterpreterInterface** | `CodeInterpreterExpansion` marker | Missing | Low |\n| **Expansion hooks** | `generated_expansion.go` with `AgentRuntimeExpansion` and `CodeInterpreterExpansion` types | Missing | Low |\n| **Fake clients** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/` | Missing | Low |\n\n---\n\n### 🧪 Test Status\n\n- **picod tests**: ✅ All 23 tests passing\n- **client package**: ✅ Builds successfully (no test files)\n\n---\n\n### Recommendation\n\nThe implementation satisfies the functional requirements for AR-015 (PicoD command execution). The missing items (`Discovery()`, `NewForConfigAndClient`, expansion hooks, fake clients) are optional enhancements typical in generated Kubernetes clients but not required for core functionality.\n\nTo fully match the spec, consider:\n1. Adding `Discovery()` method to Interface (or remove from spec)\n2. Adding `NewForConfigAndClient` constructor\n3. Adding expansion interfaces in `generated_expansion.go`\n4. Adding fake clients for testing","time":{"start":1775853620425,"end":1775853620425}}}
